html:
Hyperlinks
You are granted a limited, nonexclusive right to create a hyperlink to the homepage or recipe home page of this Web site only, provided such link does not portray Allrecipes or any of its products and services in a false, misleading, derogatory, or otherwise defamatory manner. I'm pretty such providing a hyperlink is still consider free speech; although that they feel they force their users into controlling this is a definite negative in my book.
